## Germplasm Phenotype:
   - [CS39994]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Under a short-day photoperiod (8h light/16h dark), the atg10-1 plants developed slightly slower, bolted later, and produced 70% less seed than wild type; hypersensitive to either nitrogen or carbon deprivation; senescence and programmed cell death is initiated more quickly than in wild type.
   - [atg10-1]()&nbsp;---&nbsp;Reduced fertility (70% fewer seeds), slower bolting (late flowering) and slower growing. Increased sensitivity to nitrogen and carbon deprivation.
